\lim_{n\to\infty} \left| \frac{z^n}{3^n+1} \right|^{1/n} =  \lim_{n\to\infty} \frac{|z|}{(3^n+1)^{1/n}} = \frac{|z|}{3}, 
\lim_{n\to\infty} \left| \frac{w^n}{3^{-n}+1} \right|^{1/n} =  \lim_{n\to\infty} \frac{|w|}{(3^{-n}+1)^{1/n}} = \frac{|w|}{1}, 
